{"body": "A Law to Provide for the Establishment of the Plateau State Internal Revenue Service, Administration and Collection of Revenue of All State Government Ministries, Department and Agencies; Harmonize the Rates and Levies for Collection by Local Government Councils in Plateau State and Other Matters Connected. 1 Citation and Commencement This Bill may be cited as the Plateau State Revenue (Consolidation) Law, 2017 and shall come into operation on the ninth day of August 2017.", "num": "1", "path": "library|Plateau State Revenue (Consolidation) Law, 2017|I|1", "title": "1 Citation and Commencement", "url": "/ng/plateau/justice/laws/2017/revenue/1"}
