{"body": "A Law to Provide for the Establishment of the Plateau State Internal Revenue Service, Administration and Collection of Revenue of All State Government Ministries, Department and Agencies; Harmonize the Rates and Levies for Collection by Local Government Councils in Plateau State and Other Matters Connected. PART III APPOINTMENT OF FUNCTIONARIES OF THE SERVICE, BOARD AND COMMITTEE. 17 Executive Chairman of the Service 18 Secretary to the Board", "num": "III", "path": "library|Plateau State Revenue (Consolidation) Law, 2017|III", "title": "PART III APPOINTMENT OF FUNCTIONARIES OF THE SERVICE, BOARD AND COMMITTEE.", "url": "/ng/plateau/justice/laws/2017/revenue/III"}
