{"body": "A Law to Provide for the Establishment of the Plateau State Internal Revenue Service, Administration and Collection of Revenue of All State Government Ministries, Department and Agencies; Harmonize the Rates and Levies for Collection by Local Government Councils in Plateau State and Other Matters Connected. PART V FINANCIAL PROVISIONS 21 Funds of the Service 22 Proceeds of the Fund 23 Annual Estimates and Accounts 24 Annual Reports, etc 25 Power to accept gifts 26 Power to borrow 27 Investment", "num": "V", "path": "library|Plateau State Revenue (Consolidation) Law, 2017|V", "title": "PART V FINANCIAL PROVISIONS", "url": "/ng/plateau/justice/laws/2017/revenue/V"}
