{"body": "A Law to Provide for the Establishment of the Plateau State Internal Revenue Service, Administration and Collection of Revenue of All State Government Ministries, Department and Agencies; Harmonize the Rates and Levies for Collection by Local Government Councils in Plateau State and Other Matters Connected. 61 Appeals to the Tax Appeal Committee, etc A taxable person aggrieved by an assessment made on him may appeal to the Committee within 30 days after the date of service of Notice of Refusal of the Service to amend the assessment as desired.", "num": "61", "path": "library|Plateau State Revenue (Consolidation) Law, 2017|VII|61", "title": "61 Appeals to the Tax Appeal Committee, etc", "url": "/ng/plateau/justice/laws/2017/revenue/61"}
