{"body": "A Law to Provide for the Establishment of the Plateau State Internal Revenue Service, Administration and Collection of Revenue of All State Government Ministries, Department and Agencies; Harmonize the Rates and Levies for Collection by Local Government Councils in Plateau State and Other Matters Connected. 62 Appeal to Tax Appeal Committee Where the taxable person is not satisfied with the decision of the Service, such person may appeal to the Committee.", "num": "62", "path": "library|Plateau State Revenue (Consolidation) Law, 2017|VII|62", "title": "62 Appeal to Tax Appeal Committee", "url": "/ng/plateau/justice/laws/2017/revenue/62"}
